description: This hall of fame Sakura purrs with a rating of 76, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 380, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 3 for North, 8 for East, Stringalong for South, and Stringalong for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [380 Votes, Hall of Fame]
